Pico de Gallo

1 tomato, diced
1 white onion, diced
½ fresh jalapeño, diced
½ lime, juiced
¼ cup cilantro, chopped
1 garlic clove, chopped
¼ teaspoon cumin
salt
black pepper

Makes four servings of salsa.

Combine everything including salt and pepper to taste in a bowl and mix well. Refrigerate for 10 minutes to let flavors set.

Serve chilled with tortilla chips.
